  "description": "The superconsole crate provides a handler and building blocks for powerful, yet minimally intrusive TUIs.  It is cross platform, supporting Windows 7+, Linux, and MacOS.  Rustaceans who want to create non-interactive TUIs can use the component composition building block system to quickly deploy their code.",
